title: Are They Selling?
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon discuss if the Snyders considering to sell the Commanders is something or nothing, if they believe in the Phillies now that they’re up 2-1 in the World Series and Booger McFarland joins the show for 5 Good Minutes.
